  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 400f (200c).",
    "wrap beef slices in lotus leaves and roast for 15 minutes.",
    "meanwhile, mix sunflower seeds and poppy seeds with garlic, dill, and 1 tsp of black pepper.",
    "fry kale in coconut oil until crispy, then season with salt and apple cider vinegar.",
    "assemble the wrap with roasted beef, fried kale, and the seed mixture.",
    "drizzle with honey if desired."
